# Fact Tables

## fact_sales

Purpose

Stores every product sold.

Business Event

A customer purchases a product.

Grain

One row per product sold in an order.

Composite Business Key

- order_id
- order_item_id

Foreign Keys

- customer_id
- product_id
- seller_id

Measures

- price
- freight_value
- total_item_cost

Additional Attributes

- order_status
- delivery_status
- purchase_timestamp
- shipping_limit_date
- delivery_dates

Business Questions

- Total Revenue
- Sales Trend
- Revenue by Product
- Revenue by Seller
- Delivery Performance

---

## fact_payments

Purpose

Stores payment transactions.

Business Event

Customer payment.

Grain

One payment transaction.

Composite Business Key

- order_id
- payment_sequential

Measures

- payment_value
- payment_installments

Business Questions

- Payment Type Distribution
- Installment Analysis
- Payment Trends

---

## fact_reviews

Purpose

Stores customer reviews.

Business Event

Customer submits a review.

Grain

One review record.

Business Identifier

- review_id
- order_id

Note

The source dataset does not provide a unique natural primary key for reviews because duplicate review_id and order_id combinations exist.

Measures

- review_score

Business Questions

- Average Rating
- Rating by Category
- Rating by Seller
- Customer Satisfaction
